metadata.name: down in the holler
metadata.description:
e9Art - Just Doin’ My Own Thing

ain’t got no trainin’

ain’t got no education

ain’t got no common sense

what i DO have is a hyper-active imagination that i can’t shut off

and an unquenchable curiosity

and a fire in my belly to become a better artist

to become a better ME

so here i am

again

and again

and again

just doin’ my own damn thing …

digital 1/1 art by e9Art using disco diffusion v5.1 and photoshop, April 2022 … 15000x9000 72dpi
